lockquote>張寶兒裝前裝後都完勝對手</blockquote><br />\n三個入面最唔順眼係佢喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢條眉直係天生?睇落似紋左"},{"pid":"f202498afa74d6fbb4938da691bb4038adec1941","tid":374744,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:24:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔識睇，有冇教學</blockquote><br />\n想要咩教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點睇有冇化</blockquote><br />\n除非天生皮膚好好無瑕疵，如果唔係你見啲女仔膚色好均勻紅潤嘅，通常都化咗底妝（讀緊書嘅例外），其次睇下有無內眼線同睫毛液嗰啲，仲有就係眉毛，你睇馮盈盈飄咗眉之後好睇咗幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男仔就通常要見到有眼影顏色/明顯胭脂/假眼睫毛/大紅唇色先覺得個女仔有化妝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搭單一問<br />\n想知既係條女如果無妝會係咩樣<br />\n要點推斷"},{"pid":"180c519057dc5514f63f5ba1462885de80266d7e","tid":374744,"uid":34419,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:34:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>10A都唔係賣樣啦，化唔化都係咁</blockquote><br />\n又唔使成日提住10A嘅，當娛樂節目睇下啲港姐玩化妝啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本唔係麥明詩提自己10A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係記者同連登仔成日提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf2ed040b9bad69ddb630d20180937cbc357384b","tid":374744,"uid":84381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:38:59.000Z","msg":"馮盈盈放左好多，幾可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f0f240ed7db86981a08028a7145a8ec2235fdf","tid":374744,"uid":41238,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:39:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馮盈盈放左好多，幾可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢不嬲都好放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb4a26706ccc6e6c8624df4005b5a3abbbce1a0","tid":374744,"uid":7275,"like":3,"dislik