\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見佢個妹依家選港姐好似理得你結果係點<br />\n我反正坐定粒六入tvb咁既款就 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586df87a92cdbbfebbfdab0cd22fe818ecad1a6d","tid":374744,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:53:51.000Z","msg":"化個妝樓主都講到咁深<br />\n唔識聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}